               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) The Sǝnkǝssar for the first half of the year (fols. 3ra-226vc)&#xD;
                     I-1) Maskaram (fols. 3ra-38rc)&#xD; I-2) Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 38va-69vc)&#xD; I-3)
